{"tid":1499823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰航空：#吳敏兒不是國泰航空員工#","createTime":"2019-08-24T01:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T01:45:59.000Z","uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75ecc2f7492950e1a12e6c21a8686cfae245889a","tid":1499823,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:23:51.000Z","msg":"據國泰航空官方微博23日下午消息，針對近期關於香港職工盟主席吳敏兒就國泰航空發表的言論，國泰航空發佈聲明稱：1.職工盟及其屬下的空勤人員總工會，均與國泰航空公司無關。2.吳敏兒女士不是國泰航空員工。吳女士的觀點及言論並不代表國泰航空的立場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VdGYKXx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVdGYKXx.jpg&h=d350acf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fa94abded7ae97ff3509d7d99b12c280a64b88","tid":1499823,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58cd9cf3a0bfaa2cac0ab131881ae14b0f4f030","tid":1499823,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:30:10.000Z","msg":"國泰：東方記者並非國泰員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ce30a1f01b2640f23177